title: Star Trek Antithesis (2012) - deLimited Productions Fanedit [720
description:
Summary: This edited version of Star Trek Nemesis is an attempt to peel away the non-Trek layers, and in the process reshape the overall experience of the final TNG film. For one faneditor, Nemesis always felt out of place and orphaned as a movie installment, but he wondered if the movie could be contorted to feel more like First Contact.
